<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Fitness guru Michelle Bridges has welcomed a new addition to the family. </p>

<p>On Wednesday, the 49-year-old brought home an adorable cavoodle puppy, which she and her son Axel, four, named Banjo.</p>

<p>Michelle shared a slew of photos of their furry friend to Instagram, and wrote: 'The Adventures of Banjo. Yes I'm crazy... but oh so in love.'</p>

<p>'I'm so in love': On Wednesday, fitness guru Michelle Bridges (right) brought home an adorable cavoodle puppy, which she and her son Axel (left) named Banjo</p>

<p>The former Biggest Loser trainer then shared a second photo of her son cuddling the pint-sized pooch. </p>

<p>She told her followers: 'Okay, I've been questioning myself, being a single parent, trying to run businesses, trying to give my son the most grounded wonderful life and run a household, as to what the %text<?php echo e('@'); ?>! I was thinking getting a puppy?'</p>

<p>Too cute! Michelle brought home adorable little cavoodle puppy that she and son Axel, four, named Banjo - presumably after poet, Banjo Paterson</p>

<p>She finished the caption: 'This photo answers it.' </p>

<p>Michelle has been running her business empire from Bowral, after moving out of her former marital home in Sydney earlier this year following her split from ex-partner Steve 'Commando' Willis.</p>

<p>But the ex-Biggest Loser star hasn't let her training regimen slip, and flaunted her toned torso while shooting promotional content for her activewear range, MB Active, last month.</p>

<p>Bonding: 'Ok. I've been questioning myself, being a single parent, trying to run businesses, trying to give my son the most grounded wonderful life and run a household, as to what the %text<?php echo e('@'); ?>! I was thinking getting a puppy?!?!??!!!??,' Michelle wrote</p>

<p>'Back at it! And SO happy to be too! Today's photo shoot was for my new range... it’s form meets tech meets cool,' she captioned her post shared to Instagram.   </p>

<p>In the accompanying snap, Michelle showed of her toned physique in a maroon crop top and matching leggings. </p>

<p>The mother of one looked ageless wearing flawless foundation, pale pink eyeshadow and lashings of mascara.   </p>

<p>Fab physique: Michelle got down to business last month, shooting for her new MB Active range</p>

<p>It follows a tumultuous year for Michelle, who split from Commando in January.</p>

<p>The couple began dating in 2015, after splitting from their respective partners, and welcomed their son, Axel in December that year.</p>

<p>They announced their split in January this year. After their break-up, Michelle was arrested for drink driving on Australia Day and was later convicted. </p>

<p>The way they were: Michelle and Commando (pictured) began dating in 2015, after splitting from their respective partners, and welcomed son, Axel in December that year. The couple announced their shock split in January</p>

<p>She was fined $750 and had her licence disqualified for three months, after pleading guilty to mid-range drink driving.</p>

<p>A tearful Michelle said outside court: 'I would like to take this opportunity to express my deep remorse, shame and humiliation [over] this incident and extreme lack of judgment.</p>

<p>'I would like to apologise to my family, friends and community for this gross error in judgment and the consequences of these actions will haunt me forever.'</p>

